Referencia ventana de Quartz "limpia" BP430

clear all
path='C:\Users\investigator\Google Drive\RGM-SSABAT\TOPATU_SYSTEM\Medidas\20210217';
N_imagenes= 44;
Imagen = zeros(2048);
Imagen_QUARTZ_BP430 = zeros(2048);
for n= 1:N_imagenes
file_name = [path,'\20210217_QUARTZ_1000_ms_OFFSET_m100_BP430_',num2str(n,'%05u'),'.tif'];
Imagen = 0.48.*double(imagen_Hamamatsu(file_name));
Imagen_QUARTZ_BP430 = (Imagen_QUARTZ_BP430.*(n-1)+Imagen)./n;
end
imagesc_RGM(Imagen_QUARTZ_BP430,'error');
title('BP430 config.')
line([1,2048],[925,925],'Color','r')
line([1111,1111],[1,2048],'Color','k')
plot(Imagen_QUARTZ_BP430(925,:),'r')
xlim([1,2048])
ylim('auto')
plot(Imagen_QUARTZ_BP430(:,1111),'k')
xlim([1,2048])

Substraccion del background caso LP450

A = Imagen_FBI_Ba_LP450 - Imagen_QUARTZ_LP450;
imagesc_RGM(A,'error');
xlim([836 1337])
ylim([722 1117])
title('LP450 after background substraction')
Integramos distintas 치reas circulares centradas en el haz:
C = [1088,918];
ROI = ones(2048);
Radio = [20:20:500];
Offset =[15:95];
[X_i,Y_j]=meshgrid([1:2048]);
Intensidad_rel_LP450 = zeros([length(Radio),length(Offset)]);
for m=1:length(Offset)
for n=1:length(Radio)
ROI = ((X_i-C(1)).^2+(Y_j-C(2)).^2<=Radio(n).^2);
Intensidad_rel_LP450(n,m)=suma_intensidad(ROI.*A,Offset(m))./suma_intensidad(A,Offset(m));
end
end
imagesc(Offset,Radio,Intensidad_rel_LP450);colorbar
C = [1088,918];
ROI = ones(2048);
Radio_best = 40;
Offset_best = 100;
ROI = ((X_i-C(1)).^2+(Y_j-C(2)).^2<=Radio_best.^2);
imagesc_RGM(ROI.*(A-Offset_best),'error');
xlim([836 1337])
ylim([722 1117])
title('LP450 after background substraction, Offset = -100')
hold on;draw_circle(C,Radio_best,'r');hold off
Intensidad_total_LP450 = sum(ROI.*(A-Offset_best),'all')
Intensidad_total_LP450 = 3.5201e+06
Error_Intensidad_total_LP450 = sum(ROI.*Offset_best,'all')
Error_Intensidad_total_LP450 = 502500
